        Holloway says, "We're going to help you contact your people, Kira — whatever it takes."

        And just like that, the entire community mobilizes.

        Buddy provides technical specifications.

        Velvet starts growing antenna structures based on the parameters — a weird, wonderful plant-based radio tower emerging from the facility's roof.

